---
title: Indian Chicken & Chickpea Curry with Garlic Flatbreads & Yoghurt
description: Roasting an array of colourful veggies is an instant winner and a great way to boost any curry. Stir the veggies, chicken and
the chickpeas through a tomato spiced curry sauce, mild and with notes of ginger, to allow everything to blend into
one big bowl of deliciousness.
